00:14:19,690 --> 00:14:22,749
 Dyslexics can read,
 up to a point.

305
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:25,179
 But around third
 grade, if not sooner,

306
00:14:25,180 --> 00:14:27,309
 they hit the wall in
 reading development.

