00:14:27,310 --> 00:14:29,089
 Another myth is
 that people believes

308
00:14:29,090 --> 00:14:31,659
 dyslexics will never read well.

309
00:14:31,660 --> 00:14:34,589
 In fact, dyslexics can
 become excellent readers,

310
00:14:34,590 --> 00:14:37,109
 great spellers,
 wonderful writers

311
00:14:37,110 --> 00:14:40,259
 if they are given the
 proper intervention.

