00:16:17,590 --> 00:16:21,089
 all these parts with a
 child's intelligence.

343
00:16:21,090 --> 00:16:24,919
 The intelligence of a
 child is not shown by

344
00:16:24,920 --> 00:16:27,689
 whether they can
 learn to read or not.

