1006
00:47:18,890 --> 00:47:21,799
 on dyslexia, so that new
 teachers can be better

1007
00:47:21,800 --> 00:47:24,759
 prepared to meet the needs
 of all their students.

1008
00:47:24,760 --> 00:47:27,429
 With all of the dyslexia
 research that exists,

1009
00:47:27,430 --> 00:47:30,209
 there is no reason why a child
 who struggles with reading,

1010
00:47:30,210 --> 00:47:32,589
 writing, and spelling
 cannot get the help they

1011
00:47:32,590 --> 00:47:35,449
 need to become
 successful students.

1012
00:47:35,450 --> 00:47:38,379
 Please visit
 embracingdyslexia.com, where

1013
00:47:38,380 --> 00:47:41,229
 you will find links to websites
 that provide more information

1014
00:47:41,230 --> 00:47:44,159
 about dyslexia and to
 organizations that have me

1015
00:47:44,160 --> 00:47:48,189
 permission to raise the
 awareness around the world.

1016
00:47:48,190 --> 00:47:51,649
 Every child deserves the
 opportunity to be successful.

1017
00:47:51,650 --> 00:47:53,289
 We can do this.

1018
